-Não pare de filmar.
-Droga!

1128
01:41:20,875 --> 01:41:22,208
Droga! Droga!

1129
01:41:23,708 --> 01:41:25,041
Meu Deus!

1130
01:41:34,750 --> 01:41:37,000
<i>7-L-7, responda.</i>

1131
01:41:39,666 --> 01:41:41,041
<i>7-L-7, responda.</i>

1132
01:41:41,083 --> 01:41:42,708
Desligue o carro.

1133
01:42:06,583 --> 01:42:09,666
Ele está morto.
Venha filmar.

1134
01:42:24,500 --> 01:42:25,833
Mãos firmes.

1135
01:42:30,916 --> 01:42:33,125
Use o zoom.

1136
